        <num>CC 1602</num>
        <heading>1602.  Discharge of an unsatisfied particular legacy</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1602.  Discharge of an unsatisfied particular legacy
Intestate successors and general and universal legatees are personally bound to discharge an unpaid particular legacy, each in proportion to the part of the estate that he receives.</p>
        </content>
